\begin{verbatim}
Dataset82
\end{verbatim}
A struct containing UFF Dataset 82 metadata.

\textbf{Fields}

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{type::Symbol}: Data set type


\item \texttt{line\_number::Int}: Trace line number


\item \texttt{num\_nodes::Int}: Number of nodes defining trace line


\item \texttt{color::Int}: Color


\item \texttt{id\_line::String}: Identification line


\item \texttt{line\_nodes::Vector\{Int\}}: Nodes defining trace line

\end{itemize}
